## ğŸ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v16+
- PostgreSQL 12+
- npm or yarn

### Installation
1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Raman071/Delivery-Website

cd foodie-express

### Install dependencies
# Backend
cd server
npm install

# Frontend
cd ../client
npm install

### Running the App
# Start the backend:
cd server
nodemon index.js

# Start the frontend:
cd client
npm start


Open http://localhost:3000 in your browser.
